    "updated_at": "2015-12-17T22:02:03Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Well, here's what I found: In `FrozenActor`'s constructor, `NeedRenderables` is set to the value of `startsRevealed`. At the end of the constructor `UpdateVisibility` is called, which overwrites `NeedRenderables` with the result of `Visible && !wasVisible`, so the value of `startsRevealed` basically never has any effect. Removing the call to `UpdateVisibility` from the constructor fixes the issue for me. I'm just not sure if it's needed for anything else, ie. if that's the right fix.\n"
